@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About | malichevsky</PageTitle>

<div class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <img src="assets/picture.png" alt="Kelly" class="profile-pic" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Hi, I'm Kelly<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
                <h2 class="h3 text-primary mb-4">Technical Philologist & Developer</h2>
                <p class="lead text-muted">
                    I am a 1st-year Philology student at the Ukrainian Humanities Institute (UHI), deeply passionate
                    about the structure of language and the logic of code.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2 mt-5">
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title h4 mb-3">The "Technical Philologist" 📖💻</h3>
                <p>
                    I position myself at the intersection of humanities and technology. My analytical mindset allows me
                    to treat linguistics with programming logic and philologist's attention to syntax and semantics.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I effectively combine deep humanistic knowledge with advanced PC mastery, striving to use my skills
                    to bridge the gap between human language and machine logic.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title h4 mb-3">Academic Journey 🎓</h3>
                <p>
                    Currently pursuing a degree in <strong>Philology (B11)</strong> at UHI in Bucha (September 2025 –
                    Present). My primary focus is on English Language and Literature, with a strong interest in
                    translation theory and practice.
                </p>
                <ul class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>English Language & Literature</li>
                    <li>Translation & Interpretation</li>
                    <li>Grammar Analysis & Linguistics</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt-4">
            <h3 class="card-title h4 mb-4 text-center">Beyond the Code 🛠️</h3>
            <div class="grid-3">
                <div class="text-center p-3">
                    <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🖥️</span>
                    <h5 class="mt-2">PC Power User</h5>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Expert in MS Office, Google Docs, and open-source office suites for
                        educational materials.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-3">
                    <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🔍</span>
                    <h5 class="mt-2">Data Analyst</h5>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Adept at advanced internet search and deep analysis for research
                        projects.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-3">
                    <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🤝</span>
                    <h5 class="mt-2">Adaptive Learner</h5>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Taking an individual approach to learning and providing accessible
                        explanations for complex topics.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .grid-3 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
</style>
